org.apache.river.mercury.proxy

Class MailboxProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.mercury.proxy.MailboxProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Administrable, EventMailbox, PullEventMailbox, net.jini.export.ProxyAccessor, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid

    public class MailboxProxy
extends Object
implements PullEventMailbox, Administrable, Serializable, net.jini.id.ReferentUuid, net.jini.export.ProxyAccessor
    A MailboxProxy is a proxy for the event mailbox service. This is the object passed to clients of this service. It implements the PullEventMailbox and the Administrable interfaces.
    Since:
    1.1
    Author:
    Sun Microsystems, Inc.
